#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.spacing.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.spacing"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.spacing.spacing:1 of
msgid "Return the distance between x and the nearest adjacent number."
msgstr "返回 x 与最近邻数字之间的距离。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.spacing.spacing of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.spacing.spacing:3 of
msgid "Values to find the spacing of."
msgstr "要查找间距的值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.spacing.spacing:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，则其形状必须可以广播到输入的形状。"
"如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）"
"的长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.spacing.spacing:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 的值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 的值表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.spacing.spacing of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.spacing.spacing:15 of
msgid "**out** -- The spacing of values of `x1`."
msgstr "**out** -- `x1` 值的间距。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.spacing.spacing of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.spacing.spacing:19 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.spacing.spacing:20 of
msgid ""
"It can be considered as a generalization of EPS: ``spacing(mt.float64(1))"
" == mt.finfo(mt.float64).eps``, and there should not be any representable"
" number between ``x + spacing(x)`` and x for any finite x."
msgstr ""
"它可以被看作是 EPS 的推广：``spacing(mt.float64(1)) == mt.finfo(mt."
"float64).eps``，对于任何有限的 x，``x + spacing(x)`` 和 x 之间不应存在"
"任何可表示的数字。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.spacing.spacing:25 of
msgid "Spacing of +- inf and NaN is NaN."
msgstr "+-inf 和 NaN 的间距为 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.spacing.spacing:28 of
